HEADWORD: Protyle
<hw>Pro"tyle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Proto-</ets> +
Gr. <?/ stuff, material.]</ety> <fld>(Chem. & Astron.)</fld> <def>The
hypothetical homogeneous cosmic material of the original universe,
supposed to have been differentiated into what are recognized as
distinct chemical elements.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

